			<h4>will <span>On Monday, August 6 at 8:02 am</span></h4>
			<p>I would for sure eat this&#8211;I love Pasta Primavera.  Father of three married for 15 years here saying, &#8220;I LOVE THIS STUFF.&#8221;  Although I&#8217;ve not made this version (I&#8217;m throwing my version out and just saying that I&#8217;ve always made THIS) I have added grilled chicken  to the primavera and loved it too.</p>
<p>Have you ever tried blanching your carrots and broccoli in the boiling pasta water?  You could just pop them in and let them cook for two minutes or until they pop their color, take them out and throw them in when you add all of the other sauted veggies.  </p>
<p>Some of your Triamisu and a super buttery, garlicky, five cheese toast would be all I need for total satisfaction.  Thanks for sharing.</p>
<p>By the way, has your Albertson&#8217;s changed names?  My Albertsons is now Food Pyramid!  What the heck kind of name is that for a grocery store?  It sounds like I&#8217;m talking to the school nutritionist.</p>
					</div>
