Kill 2 birds with 1 chef&#8217;s knife!  Take your garlic cloves and whack them hard with the blade (use your palm to press down hard on the clove) and it&#8217;ll peel them and smash them in one move.  It&#8217;s the easiest way to peel garlic!</p>
